nnoremap <leader>] /]<ESC>
nnoremap <leader>( /(<ESC>
nnoremap <leader>) /)<ESC>

" Open new window on right and then open a NERDTree window
nnoremap <leader>vs :vsplit<ESC>:wincmd l<CR>:NERDTree<CR>

